# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# E2E test scaffolding (regression suite + Sprint 6 specs) is CHECKED IN.
# Per docs_sprint6/E2E_PLAYWRIGHT_SCENARIOS_SPRINT1_6.md + AGENTS.md §4 TDD rule,
# every Sprint task must ship a Playwright spec — they are source-of-truth test code
# under web/e2e/{smoke,support}/ and web/e2e/run-smoke.sh.
# Generated run-time artifacts (playwright-report/, test-results/, *.trace, *.tmp
# under web/e2e/) are excluded via the root .gitignore + the explicit patterns below.

node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

# Exclude generated artifacts INSIDE the committed e2e/ tree (per CI runs).
**/e2e/playwright-report
**/e2e/test-results
**/e2e/**/*.tmp
**/e2e/**/*.trace

# Editor directories and files
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea
.DS_Store
*.suo
*.ntvs*
*.njsproj
*.sln
*.sw?
